<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>System Interruption — Berani Cerdas</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #0b0f19;
    }
    .glow-error {
      box-shadow: 0 0 50px -10px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
    }
    .text-gradient-error {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f87171 0%, #dc2626 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 relative overflow-hidden selection:bg-red-500/30 selection:text-red-200">

  <div class="absolute top-[30%] left-[50%] translate-x-[-50%] translate-y-[-50%] w-[450px] h-[450px] rounded-full bg-red-900/10 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="w-full max-w-md z-10">
    <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-red-500/20 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 text-center glow-error transition-all duration-300">
      
      <div class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-red-400 text-2xl shadow-inner">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation animate-pulse"></i>
      </div>

      <h1 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">
        Sistem <span class="text-gradient-error">Gagal Transmisi</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mb-6 text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed max-w-sm mx-auto">
        Infrastruktur gagal memproses pengiriman pesan broadcast massal. Pastikan sinkronisasi database Supabase Anda aktif dan token bot Telegram dikonfigurasi secara valid di file 
        <code class="bg-slate-950 px-2 py-1 rounded border border-slate-800 font-mono text-[10px] text-red-400">.env</code>.
      </p>

      <div class="border-t border-slate-800/80 pt-6">
        <a href="/admin" class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500/10 to-red-600/20 border border-red-500/30 px-6 py-4 text-xs font-bold text-red-400 transition hover:bg-red-500 hover:text-white hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left text-[10px]"></i> Kembali ke Dashboard Admin
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-600 tracking-wider">
        SYS_STATUS: 500_INTERNAL_BROADCAST_EXCEPTION
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>